2 Date: (Filing No. S- )
3 HEALTH AND HUMAN SERVICES
5 STATE OF MAINE
6 SENATE
7 132ND LEGISLATURE
8 FIRST SPECIAL SESSION
9 COMMITTEE AMENDMENT “ ” to S.P. 729, L.D. 1859, “An Act to Improve
10 Access to Child Care and Early Childhood Education by Establishing Regional Resource
11 Hubs”
12 Amend the bill in section 1 in c. 1083 in §4100-D in subsection 3 in the first line (page
13 1, line 19 in L.D.) by striking out the following: "November 1, 2025" and inserting the
14 following: 'July 1, 2026'
15 Amend the bill in section 1 in c. 1083 in §4100-D in subsection 3 in the first line (page
16 1, line 19 in L.D.) by striking out the following: "4" and inserting the following: '2'
17 Amend the bill in section 1 in c. 1083 in §4100-D in subsection 3 in paragraph B in the
18 first line (page 1, line 24 in L.D.) by inserting after the following: "the" the following:
19 'Maine'
20 Amend the bill in section 1 in c. 1083 in §4100-D in subsection 3 in paragraph B in the
21 first line (page 1, line 24 in L.D.) by inserting after the following: "Cabinet" the following:
22 'Early Childhood Advisory Council'
23 Amend the bill in section 1 in c. 1083 in §4100-D in subsection 3 in paragraph B in the
24 first line (page 1, line 24 in L.D.) by striking out the following: "19131" and inserting the
25 following: '24051'
26 Amend the bill in section 1 in c. 1083 in §4100-D in subsection 7 in the first line (page
27 3, line 38 in L.D.) by striking out the following: "2027" and inserting the following: '2028'
28 Amend the bill in section 2 in the first line (page 4, line 6 in L.D.) by striking out the
29 following: "December 15, 2025" and inserting the following: 'March 15, 2026'
30 Amend the bill in section 2 in the 3rd line (page 4, line 8 in L.D.) by inserting after the
31 following: "department's" the following: 'written'
32 Amend the bill in section 2 in the 4th line (page 4, line 9 in L.D.) by striking out the
33 following: "4" and inserting the following: '2'
34 Amend the bill by striking out all of section 3 and inserting the following:
